He was sent to the dentist an hour ago.
Tooth ache.

427
29:51.798 --> 29:52.900
Tooth ache.

428
29:53.000 --> 29:55.298
Yes tooth ache. But nothing serious.

429
29:55.500 --> 29:57.400
He will be back in the evening.

430
29:57.798 --> 30:01.500
