431
30:01.798 --> 30:04.000
Can I pass you something for him?

432
30:04.700 --> 30:06.200
Of course.

433
30:09.200 --> 30:12.500
Her name is Violette, Violette Morange

434
30:12.798 --> 30:15.700
Single mother. Despairing over her son's attitude.

435
30:15.798 --> 30:20.500
Prone to stealing, introvert.
Expelled from a few schools for running away.

436
30:21.000 --> 30:24.400
When Pierre was sent to Pond Bottom
against his mother's will,

437
