35:25.800 --> 35:29.699
Feb. 8, first rehearsals.
Rachin is relentless on Morange

518
35:30.300 --> 35:35.199
After jail, he makes an example out of him:
one month of community service.

519
35:58.699 --> 36:00.599
Hey, maid, don't forget to make my bed!

