36:35.300 --> 36:36.599
Feb. 15

521
36:36.699 --> 36:39.400
A visit from Dr. Dervaux. He is a psychologist

522
36:39.699 --> 36:42.099
He brought us a little present.

523
36:42.099 --> 36:46.000
We decided to bring this boy from St Fereol's juvenile detention centre.

524
36:46.199 --> 36:51.199
To study his capacity to adapt to a more liberal environment.

525
36:52.000 --> 36:55.900
Unlike most of his classmates,
Mondain is starting to read and write.

526
36:56.099 --> 36:57.800
In any case, he can talk

527
36:58.000 --> 36:59.400
More or less normally.

528
36:59.599 --> 37:02.699
We submitted his intellect
to the Binet-Simon test

529
37:02.900 --> 37:04.498
Ah, the Binet-Simon test!

530
37:04.500 --> 37:07.400
We also gave him Rorchar's test

531
37:07.599 --> 37:08.797
Good.

532
37:08.800 --> 37:12.300
The test, as you know,
divides children's intelligent into 7 categories.

533
37:12.400 --> 37:17.199
Normal, adequate, borderline,
Slightly retarded, medium, severely retarded

534
37:17.500 --> 37:20.400
And finally, imbeciles

535
37:20.599 --> 37:23.199
Mondain is in the borderline zone.

536
37:23.199 --> 37:27.099
He is therefore not demented. I must however warn you.

537
37:28.099 --> 37:31.800
He exhibit gregarious-instinct pervert tendencies.

538
37:33.900 --> 37:35.500
Bad enough.

539
37:35.699 --> 37:37.400
What exactly does that mean?

540
37:37.500 --> 37:40.599
Doctor?

541
37:40.800 --> 37:45.800
Prone to cruelty, parasitism and destruction. Above all,

542
37:46.000 --> 37:48.300
Mythomania
There you have it.

