Isolation over

578
39:53.699 --> 39:56.500
I brought Pepinot back. You forgot him by the gate.

579
39:56.699 --> 39:59.699
Pepinot, it's not Saturday today.

580
40:01.699 --> 40:04.900
By the way, in the letters to your parents

581
40:05.099 --> 40:06.800
I don't have any parents.

582
40:07.400 --> 40:09.199
Of course, to those who have parents

583
40:09.300 --> 40:12.900
Remind them that they can visit you on
the first or third Thursday of the month.

584
40:13.000 --> 40:17.400
Morange, you are already distracted.
What did I just say?

585
40:17.699 --> 40:18.699
I don't know.

586
40:19.000 --> 40:20.699
I just said, you can write to your mother

587
40:20.800 --> 40:23.300
To visit you on the first or third Thursday every month.

588
40:24.300 --> 40:26.800
