590
40:30.800 --> 40:32.400
But Morange may want to see his mother.

591
40:32.400 --> 40:34.300
Maybe he's not the only one.

592
40:37.099 --> 40:39.599
See, Morange, we have a real choir now.

593
40:39.800 --> 40:41.099
I don't care.

594
40:41.199 --> 40:42.699
